478
00:29:47,619 --> 00:29:49,390
- Great job.
- Great work today.

479
00:29:54,799 --> 00:29:55,930
Great work.

480
00:30:03,210 --> 00:30:04,509
You're very difficult,

481
00:30:05,279 --> 00:30:06,279
Anchor Lee.

482
00:30:08,440 --> 00:30:11,279
You always seem to tell the truth,

483
00:30:12,250 --> 00:30:14,119
