484
00:30:16,349 --> 00:30:18,289
I hear a lot from you,

485
00:30:19,019 --> 00:30:20,920
but it seems like I heard nothing.

486
00:30:23,730 --> 00:30:25,329
It's frustrating at times,

487
00:30:27,359 --> 00:30:28,900
but I keep wanting to know more.

488
00:30:31,200 --> 00:30:32,670
I find you very difficult,

489
00:30:33,440 --> 00:30:34,700
Anchor Lee.

490
00:30:39,609 --> 00:30:41,210
(Tae Eun)

491
00:30:50,789 --> 00:30:52,690
What suddenly brings you here?

492
00:30:53,259 --> 00:30:54,960
I caused a bit of an accident.

493
00:30:55,660 --> 00:30:56,730
Like what?

494
00:30:57,190 --> 00:30:59,599
Ha Jin found out...

495
00:30:59,930 --> 00:31:01,230
about your disease.

496
00:31:03,299 --> 00:31:04,369
It's my mistake.

497
00:31:04,569 --> 00:31:07,539
I once mentioned you
during our session.

498
00:31:07,539 --> 00:31:10,640
It was just once,
but she remembered it.

499
00:31:13,339 --> 00:31:14,410
I'm sorry.

500
00:31:15,279 --> 00:31:17,180
It's not your fault
I have that disease.

501
00:31:18,210 --> 00:31:20,849
There's no reason
to hide it from everyone forever.

502
00:31:21,420 --> 00:31:22,490
So...

503
00:31:23,289 --> 00:31:26,190
how much does she know
about her condition?

504
00:31:26,819 --> 00:31:29,490
Why does she think
there's a problem with her memory?

505
00:31:30,190 --> 00:31:31,460
A motorcycle accident.

506
00:31:32,329 --> 00:31:33,559
She thinks she got badly hurt...

507
00:31:33,559 --> 00:31:36,829
because of that accident,
fell unconscious, then woke up,

508
00:31:37,369 --> 00:31:40,940
and that it caused a momentary
problem with her memory.

509
00:31:41,200 --> 00:31:42,470
That's what she knows.

510
00:31:43,869 --> 00:31:44,940
By any chance,

511
00:31:45,839 --> 00:31:49,079
did she ever tell you
about her condition?

512
00:31:49,609 --> 00:31:51,509
I heard she said she isn't normal.

513
00:31:53,150 --> 00:31:54,150
Yes.

514
00:31:55,490 --> 00:31:58,319
She still thinks
there's a problem with her memory.

515
00:31:58,920 --> 00:32:00,490
And she seems to be confused.

516
00:32:01,119 --> 00:32:02,759
Why didn't you tell me?

517
00:32:02,759 --> 00:32:04,990
It seemed like
she didn't want others to find out.

518
00:32:06,259 --> 00:32:08,970
I can't tell you
something she wants to hide.

519
00:32:13,099 --> 00:32:14,700
To be honest, I'm nervous...

520
00:32:15,440 --> 00:32:18,039
that things will
get out of our hands.

521
00:32:18,039 --> 00:32:19,240
If...

522
00:32:20,039 --> 00:32:21,940
she remembers Seo Yeon,

523
00:32:22,380 --> 00:32:24,349
you also know what could happen.

524
00:32:24,880 --> 00:32:28,319
I don't want to see you
or Ha Jin get hurt.

525
00:32:29,190 --> 00:32:30,619
Don't do anything you'll regret.

526
00:32:31,089 --> 00:32:32,390
I'm doing my best.

527
00:32:33,019 --> 00:32:35,430
I also don't want her to be hurt.

528
00:32:36,390 --> 00:32:37,630
Don't worry.
